imdb.plot outline: Do you live and breathe soccer? Are you eagerly anticipating the next game? Is soccer your life - or at least a big part of it? If your answer is Yes. Then the YouTube Channel All Your Living Needs is for you. As the host of the channel, Johno makes predictions each week on how teams will do in the English Premier League and Major League Soccer.
imdb.title: All Your Living Needs
